narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It seemed to be a lot easier for those who took spanish before in high school than those who began spanish last semester in the fall as a freshman.
I would definitely recommend Spanish 120 05 to another student. Spanish is made more fun and you definitely learn it.
You'll learn a lot, but be prepared to work.
Take it! Well taught class, and an easy way to get that extra half of a credit.
